# Robowen

> Robowen is the iOS development work of Robert Owen, an indie developer based in the UK.
> Apps include Stylus (daily task manager for iOS), Octoscope (Octopus Energy data for iOS/iPadOS/watchOS/macOS),
> OctoPump (heat-pump controller for UK households on the Octopus Energy Cosy tariff),
> HomeUI (HomeKit and Matter dashboard for Apple Vision Pro), and Darkfield (astronomy companion for
> iPhone, iPad, and Mac). This site hosts the developer blog, app landing pages, and press materials.

## Apps

- [Stylus]({{ metadata.url }}apps/stylus/): Mindful daily task manager for iOS — prioritise, refine, and make progress on what matters without endless lists.
- [Octoscope]({{ metadata.url }}apps/octoscope/): Octopus Energy data app for iPhone, iPad, Apple Watch, and Mac — explore usage, pricing, and carbon emissions with widgets and Shortcuts support.
- [OctoPump]({{ metadata.url }}apps/octopump/): Heat-pump controller for UK households on the Octopus Energy Cosy tariff — automatically schedules heating around the daily off-peak windows.
- [HomeUI]({{ metadata.url }}apps/homeui/): Rich HomeKit app for Apple Vision Pro — live camera feeds and interactive 2D/3D controls for scenes, lights, and accessories.
- [Darkfield]({{ metadata.url }}apps/darkfield/): Astronomy companion for iPhone, iPad, and Mac — track your stargazing sessions in one place.

